.welcome-tour-bg
.rounded.p4.remodal-wt#first{data:{"remodal-id":"modal-0"}}
  %a.skip-for-now.absolute.top-0.right-0.p2.pointer{class: "#{'hidden' if @tour}", data: {step: 0}}
    %img.icon-m{src: "/fat_icons/i-close.svg"}
  = image_tag "i-earth", class:"col-4 sm-col-3"
  %h2.sm-h1.medium.mb0 Welcome, #{@profile.first_name}!
  .h5.sm-h4.measure.mx-auto.mt1.mb6
    %p.my0.left-align We all want to make a positive impact on the environment. But where do you start? MyDomino makes it easy to lower your carbon footprint, starting with small steps.
  .wt-next.btn.btn-md.btn-primary.btn-primary--hover.mb2{data: {step: 0}} What's my carbon footprint?

.rounded.p4.remodal-wt#second{style: 'display: none;', data:{"remodal-id":"modal-1"}}
  = image_tag "illo-balloon", class:"col-5 sm-col-4"
  %a.skip-for-now.absolute.top-0.right-0.p2.pointer{class: "#{'hidden' if @tour}", data: {step: 1}}
    %img.icon-m{src: "/fat_icons/i-close.svg"}
  %h2.sm-h1.medium.mt1.mb0 Carbon Footprint
  .h5.sm-h4.measure.mx-auto.left-align.mt1
    %span Did you know that the average American produces enough carbon emissions each day to fill a
    %span.bold 12-foot-wide balloon?
    %span Every small choice you make enlarges or shrinks this balloon (your carbon footprint)!
    %p.mt2.mb2
      %span Managing these choices can be overwhelming. So we broke it down into simple steps you can take in your
      %span.bold food, transportation, and energy.
    .h5.sm-h4.measure.mx-auto.mt2
      .flex.justify-center.bg-orange--light.px1.py2.rounded
        .flex.flex-column.items-center.mx3
          = image_tag "icons/i-apple--outline", class:"icon-xl"
          Food
        .flex.flex-column.items-center
          = image_tag "icons/i-scooter", class:"icon-xl"
          Transportation
        .flex.flex-column.items-center.mx3
          = image_tag "icons/i-lightbulb", class:"icon-xl"
          Energy
      %p.gray-5.center.mt1 These 3 areas account for 75% of your carbon emissions.

  .mt3.flex.justify-end
    .flex.items-center
      %a.wt-back.text-decoration-none.gray-6.pointer.mr3{data: {step: 1}}
        .flex.items-center
          %span.inline-block.mr1
            =inline_svg "icons/i-arrow-left.svg", class: 'icon-s fill-gray-4 block'
          .h5.gray-4 Back

      .wt-next.btn.btn-sm.btn-primary.btn-primary--hover{data: {step: 1}}
        .flex.items-center
          Next
          %span.inline-block.ml1
            = inline_svg "icons/i-arrow-right.svg", class: "icon-s fill-white block"


.remodal-wt.p4#third{style: "display: none;", data:{"remodal-id":"modal-2"}}
  %a.skip-for-now.absolute.top-0.right-0.p2.pointer{class: "#{'hidden' if @tour}", data: {step: 2}}
    %img.icon-m{src: "/fat_icons/i-close.svg"}
  = image_tag "i-impact-categories.png", class: "col-4"

  %h2.sm-h1.medium.mt1.mb0 Let's start with food

  .h5.sm-h4.measure.mx-auto.left-align.mt1.mb3
    %p.left-align.mt1.mb2
      %span.left-align
        Food contributes up to
      %span.bold 30% of our carbon emissions.
      %span It takes energy to grow, process, transport, and store our food.
    %p.left-align.my1
      The good news is that with some simple food changes, you can easily make a dent in your carbon footprint right away!

    .flex.items-center.bg-orange--light.px3.py2.rounded.mt2.mb4
      = image_tag "icons/i-apple", class:"icon-xl"
      %p.left-align.pl2
        Join the food challenge and see how much you can lower your "Carbon Foodprint."

  .mt3.flex.justify-end
    .flex.items-center
      %a.wt-back.text-decoration-none.gray-6.pointer.mr3{data: {step: 2}}
        .flex.items-center
          %span.inline-block.mr1
            =inline_svg "icons/i-arrow-left.svg", class: "icon-s fill-gray-4 block"
          .h5.gray-4 Back

      .btn.btn-sm.btn-primary.btn-primary--hover{class: "#{@mobile ? 'wt-next' : 'wt-finish'}", data: {"remodal-selector": "#third", "step": 2}}
        .flex.items-center
          Take a tour
          %span.inline-block.ml1
            = inline_svg "icons/i-arrow-right.svg", class: "icon-s fill-white block"

-if @mobile
